== Overview ==

Final Fantasy IV features numerous items including consumables, key items, and equipment. This page documents all items and their data.

== Item Data Structure ==

Item data is 16 bytes per entry:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Item type
|-
| $01 || 1 || Equip flags
|-
| $02 || 1 || Effect ID
|-
| $03 || 1 || Effect power
|-
| $04-$05 || 2 || Buy price
|-
| $06-$07 || 2 || Sell price
|-
| $08-$0F || 8 || Additional attributes
|}

